https://open-meteo.com/
https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

This prototype uses Open-Meteo's free non-commercial endpoint. A commercial deployment must move to
an appropriate paid Open-Meteo plan or a self-hosted Open-Meteo deployment and retain attribution.

Track records contain factual metadata only (title, artist, year, approximate duration and hand-curated
recommendation attributes). Track identity, spelling, year, and duration were cross-checked against the
public Apple Music/iTunes catalog and public discographies on 2026-07-12. Editorial energy, valence,
acousticness, familiarity, mood, weather, and activity values are MoodTransit estimates, not official
streaming metrics and not therapeutic claims. This repository contains no audio files, cover art, or lyrics.
Outbound music links are search URLs generated from title and artist metadata.
